name: A random passerby
description:
The photo is not staged. It was foggy that beautiful evening and I decided not to miss such a great opportunity. I took my tripod and camera and went outside to photograph the beautiful foggy landscape. Just as I was about to take a picture of the empty street, a random passerby appeared out of nowhere, thus completing my shot.

Location: Kharkiv, Ukraine
Date of photo creation: February 2, 2021
JPEG is 6000x4000 pixels
